= Documentation starting points

== Helpers

* ApplicationHelper - Global helpers
* VideoHelper - Helpers for video embeds
* Admin::AdminHelper - Helpers for Admin modules

== Models

Account, Category, Event, Feed, FeedItem, Imageset, MailSubscriber, Mailing, Mailout, 
Page, PageComment, PageFile, Partial, SetImage, SmsSubscriber, Tag, Tagging, Textbit, 
User and UserLogin.

== Mailers

AdminMailer and Notifications.

== Controllers

*Global*

* PagesCore::ApplicationController - All controllers inherit this. Provides authentication and error handling.
* ErrorsController - Renders error messages

*Frontend*

* FeedsController
* PagesController 
* PageFilesController
* XmlController - Legacy controller. The Flash API uses this.

*Admin*

* Admin::AdminController - Abstract controller for all Admin:: controllers.
* Admin::AccountsController
* Admin::CategoriesController
* Admin::FilesController
* Admin::NewsletterController
* Admin::PageFilesController
* Admin::PagesController
* Admin::PartialsController
* Admin::UsersController

*Libraries*

* Apparat - SMS service interface
* FeedBuilder - Creates RSS 2.0 feeds
* Language - Languages support
* MumboJumbo - Internationalization of strings
* PagesCore - Core libraries for Pages
* Postnummer - Norwegian postal codes



= Installation

== Dependencies

Pages requires Rails > 2.0. The following gems are required and can be 
installed from Rubyforge:

* acts_as_ferret
* BlueCloth
* enumerable_mapper
* ferret
* hpricot 
* lame_encoder 
* mp3info
* RedCloth
* simple-rss
* uuidtools 
* vector2d
	

=== Plugins

These plugins are required:
	acts_as_list        http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/resourced-plugins/acts_as_list
	acts_as_tree        http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/resourced-plugins/acts_as_tree
	engines             http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/resourced-plugins/engines
	recaptcha           http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/resourced-plugins/recaptcha
	thinking-sphinx     http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/resourced-plugins/thinking-sphinx
	dynamic_image       http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/plugins/dynamic_image/trunk
	pages               http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/plugins/pages/trunk

Some Backstage-plugins provide additional functionality, but are not required:
	pages_gallery       http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/plugins/pages_gallery/trunk
	backstage_festival  http://svn.manualdesign.no/svn/backstage/plugins/backstage_festival/trunk
